title: Storm Doris: Plane aborts landing in wind
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Storm Doris: Plane aborts landing in wind 23 February 2017 Last updated at 16:33 GMT 
Storm Doris has caused travel disruption around the UK, including the cancellation and delays for many flights. 
This passenger plane had to abandon its initial landing attempt at Manchester Airport due to high winds buffeting its approach. Read more
